# MY MENU

Access a personalized menu of frequently-used options.

To display “my menu”, press `MENU/OK` in the shooting display and select the !MY MENU Tab (MY MENU) tab.

!My Menu Display

*The MY tab is only available if options have been assigned to MY MENU.*

## MY MENU SETTING

To choose the items listed in the !MY MENU Tab (MY MENU) tab:

1. In the setup menu, select !User Setting Icon `USER SETTING` > !My Menu Setting Icon `MY MENU SETTING` or !My Menu Setting Icon `MY MENU SETTING`.

   - To reorder items, select `RANK ITEMS`.
   - To delete items, select `REMOVE ITEMS`.

   !My Menu Setting Options

2. Press the selector up or down to highlight `ADD ITEMS` and press `MENU/OK`. Options that can be added to “my menu” are highlighted in blue.

   !Add Items Menu

*Items currently in “my menu” are indicated by check marks.*
